databaseQueries.query: SELECT "users".*, (SELECT count(*) FROM "workspaces" inner join "user_workspace" on "workspaces"."id" = "user_workspace"."workspace_id" WHERE "users"."id" = "user_workspace"."user_id") as "workspaces_count" FROM "users" WHERE "id" = '2' LIMIT 1
SELECT * FROM "forms" WHERE "forms"."id" = '1' and "forms"."deleted_at" IS NULL LIMIT 1

SELECT "workspaces".*, "user_workspace"."user_id" as "pivot_user_id", "user_workspace"."workspace_id" as "pivot_workspace_id" FROM "workspaces" inner join "user_workspace" on "workspaces"."id" = "user_workspace"."workspace_id" WHERE "user_workspace"."user_id" = 2 and "workspaces"."id" = 2 LIMIT 1

SELECT "users".*, (SELECT count(*) FROM "workspaces" inner join "user_workspace" on "workspaces"."id" = "user_workspace"."workspace_id" WHERE "users"."id" = "user_workspace"."user_id") as "workspaces_count" FROM "users" WHERE "users"."id" = 2 LIMIT 1
SELECT count(*) as aggregate FROM "form_views" WHERE "form_views"."form_id" = 1 and "form_views"."form_id" IS not NULL
SELECT sum(cast(data->>'views' as integer)) as aggregate FROM "form_statistics" WHERE "form_statistics"."form_id" = 1 and "form_statistics"."form_id" IS not NULL
SELECT count(*) as aggregate FROM "form_submissions" WHERE "form_submissions"."form_id" = 1 and "form_submissions"."form_id" IS not NULL

SELECT "workspaces".*, "user_workspace"."user_id" as "pivot_user_id", "user_workspace"."workspace_id" as "pivot_workspace_id" FROM "workspaces" inner join "user_workspace" on "workspaces"."id" = "user_workspace"."workspace_id" WHERE "user_workspace"."user_id" = 2 and "workspaces"."id" = 2 LIMIT 1
SELECT * FROM "subscriptions" WHERE "subscriptions"."user_id" = 2 and "subscriptions"."user_id" IS not NULL ORDER BY "created_at" DESC

SELECT exists(SELECT * FROM "workspaces" inner join "user_workspace" on "workspaces"."id" = "user_workspace"."workspace_id" WHERE "user_workspace"."user_id" = 2 and exists (SELECT * FROM "forms" WHERE "workspaces"."id" = "forms"."workspace_id" and "forms"."deleted_at" IS NULL)) as "exists"
